# noteLang Example

A quick tour of all supported syntax elements.

---

## Inline Formatting

Normal text with **bold**, *italic*, ~~strikethrough~~, and `inline code`.

A [link to Neovim](https://neovim.io) and an image:

![Neovim logo](https://neovim.io/images/logo@2x.png)

---

## Headings

# H1 Heading
## H2 Heading
### H3 Heading
#### H4 Heading
##### H5 Heading
###### H6 Heading

---

## Lists

Unordered:

- Apples
- Bananas
  - Cavendish
  - Plantain
- Cherries

Ordered:

1. First step
2. Second step
3. Third step
   1. Sub-step A
   2. Sub-step B

---

## Blockquote

> This is a blockquote.
> It can span multiple lines and supports **inline formatting**.

---

## Code Block

```lua
local function greet(name)
  print("Hello, " .. name .. "!")
end

greet("world")
```

---

## Pipe Table

| Language | Paradigm | Year |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Lua | Multi-paradigm | 1993 |
| Rust | Systems | 2015 |
| Pythsd | High-level | 1991 |

