## Raw Mermaid

@graph {
graph TD
  A[Start] --> B{Decision}
  B -- Yes --> C[Do the thing]
  B -- No --> D[Skip it]
  C --> E[End]
  D --> E
}

---


## Table Examples


@table(2, 2){
    hello, there
    new, table
}


table(this, 2, 2) 

|hello|there|
|new|table|
